==Times and locations==
The game's locations are China, England, France, Holland, India, Italy, Japan, Mexico, Peru, Russia, Spain, and the USA.

Each location can be visited during four different time periods: 400 to 1300, 1300 to 1700, 1700 to 1900, and 1900 to the present day.

